      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"fresh perspective\" doesn't change the math. The debt is real, the failure is real, and the look on my wife's face when she finds out is gonna be something I can't live with. There's no \"coming out the other side\" when you've ruined everyone's life because of your own ego. It feels like everything I built was just a lie, and now the truth is just too heavy to carry. It feels like I'm just waiting for the floor to drop out.",
